#. module: cake_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:cake_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Odoo is entirely integrated into an App. Download it to turn your phone into "
"a tool to manage your entire workflow."
msgstr ""
"Odoo este complet integrat într-o aplicație. Descarc-o pentru a transforma "
"telefonul într-o unealtă de gestionare a întregului flux de lucru."

#. module: cake_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:cake_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid "Odoo offers endless customization possibilities for your cake shop:"
msgstr ""
"Odoo oferă posibilități nelimitate de personalizare pentru cofetăria ta:"

#. module: cake_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:cake_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Of course, this is just an overview of the features included in this "
"package. Feel free to add new apps, delete/modify demo data, and test "
"everything around!"
